---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <span class="tag sanskrit">॥ कर्मसु कौशलम् ॥</span>
            <span class="tag">Background</span>
            <h1>Professional <span class="highlight">Background</span></h1>
            <p class="lead" style="max-width: 650px;">
                My work is built on a simple observation: most visible problems are often symptoms of deeper structural issues. A website problem may be a positioning problem. A content problem may be a knowledge problem. An operational problem may be a systems problem.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 40px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
            <p>My background combines eight years of operational leadership in high-volume hospitality environments, direct client-facing sales, logistics coordination, team management, and self-directed research into systems, information architecture, and organizational design.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Professional Experience</h2>
            <div style="background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Travel Desk Operations Supervisor</h3>
                <p style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent);">Ashoka Tours and Travels (Deployed at client properties) · 2018 – 2026 · Delhi NCR</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;"><strong style="color: var(--text);">Client Sites Managed:</strong> Holiday Inn Aerocity (Front Desk), ibis Aerocity (Front Desk), Vivanta by Taj Dwarka (Front Desk), Pullman New Delhi Aerocity & Novotel New Delhi Aerocity (Car Desk — simultaneous dual-property management)</p>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 1rem;">Key Responsibilities:</h4>
                <ul class="structural">
                    <li>Managed daily travel desk operations across multiple premium properties in Aerocity and Dwarka</li>
                    <li>Coordinated guest transportation, chauffeur allocation (8–25 staff per shift), and vendor relationships</li>
                    <li>Handled guest escalations, service recovery, and cross-functional coordination with hotel departments</li>
                </ul>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 1rem;">Sales & Relationship Building:</h4>
                <ul class="structural">
                    <li>Closed 50+ premium tour packages (Jaipur-Agra-Delhi itineraries) within high-season lobby deployment windows</li>
                    <li>Highest single booking contract size: £60,000 for a 3-day / 3-night customized itinerary</li>
                    <li>Built strong repeat-guest relationships; frequently became the guest's preferred point of contact</li>
                    <li>Received independent employment offers from guests based on professional reputation</li>
                </ul>
                <h4 style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 1rem;">Logistics & Crew Coordination:</h4>
                <ul class="structural">
                    <li>IndiGo Crew Rotation: Coordinated complex crew rotations (40+ crew members using only 6 vehicles under strict airport cut-off times)</li>
                    <li>Managed crew logistics for Air Asia, Mauritius Airlines, and time-sensitive corporate transfers for DHL</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong style="color: var(--text);">Systems Exposure:</strong> OPERA PMS — hands-on experience in property management systems</p>
            </div>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">LucentHindu — 2020 – Present</h2>
            <p>LucentHindu is the operating platform where I build, test, and document systems for digital presence, knowledge management, and business operations. It functions as both my consulting foundation and a live research environment.</p>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">LucentHindu.com</strong> — Designed and developed a complete digital presence system: website architecture, information architecture, navigation, content structure, and documentation standards.</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Canon</strong> — A structured knowledge framework for understanding reality, human behavior, society, information, and institutions through recurring principles, mechanisms, and patterns.</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Independent Website Projects</strong> — Worked with micro-business clients on website structure, content organization, sitemap planning, WordPress implementation, and deployment support.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Independent Research & Applied Learning</h2>
            <p>Over the years, I have studied and applied concepts in:</p>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Systems & Operations:</strong> Systems Thinking, Process Mapping, Workflow Design, Operational Design</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Information & Knowledge:</strong> Information Architecture, Knowledge Management, Documentation Design, Content Systems</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Human & Organizational:</strong> Human Behavior, Learning Systems, Decision-Making, Organizational Design, Problem Diagnosis</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Learning has been developed through practical experience, experimentation, independent research, reading, and real-world application.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Certifications</h2>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Digital Marketing Certification</strong> — Google Digital Garage</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Advanced SEO Certification</strong> — Simplelearn</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Core Skills</h2>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Diagnostic:</strong> Systems Analysis, Problem Diagnosis, Process Mapping, Operational Assessment</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Strategic:</strong> Information Architecture, Workflow Design, Digital Strategy, Knowledge Organization</li>
                <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Technical:</strong> WordPress, SEO, Content Management Systems, Automation Tools, OPERA PMS, Video Editing Tools</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Education & Self-Directed Learning</h2>
            <p><strong style="color: var(--text);">Formal Education:</strong> Higher Secondary Education (12th Standard)</p>
            <p>Additional learning has been developed through practical experience, independent research, experimentation, and self-directed study.</p>

            <div style="margin-top: 2rem; background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem;">Contact</h2>
                <p><strong style="color: var(--text);">Website:</strong> LucentHindu.com</p>
                <p><strong style="color: var(--text);">Core Services:</strong> Systems Audits · Digital Presence Systems · Knowledge Systems · Business Systems & Automation</p>
                <p style="font-style: italic; color: var(--accent);">Every engagement begins with understanding.</p>
                <a href="/work-with-aman/systems-audit" class="btn" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Request a Systems Audit</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>